Package: xdvir
Type: Package
Title: Render DVI Files
Version: 0.1-0
Authors@R: person("Paul", "Murrell", email = "paul@stat.auckland.ac.nz",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: Paul Murrell <paul@stat.auckland.ac.nz>
Description: Functions to author TeX documents, typeset TeX documents, 
             read the resulting DVI files, and render them within R.
Depends: R (>= 4.3.0)
SystemRequirements: freetype2
Imports: grDevices, grid, hexView (>= 0.3-4), tinytex
Suggests: knitr, rmarkdown
VignetteBuilder: knitr
License: GPL-3
